column5: Went muskie fishing today with my brother and had a good day.  Tied my PB with a nice fat 44 inch muskie and then landed a 36" one later on in the day.  Usually my bro has the better day, but not today.  I know your reading this Scott (fishsevern) so all I got to say is haha.  You get none, but thanks for taking the picture bro.
Looks like you kicked butt, beauty fish  What bait were you trolling?
Nice ones, they don't come easy on the 'Upper'!
Catching your heaviest musky always makes for a great day.  Lots of energy when released.  Next time soon!
Nice fish.    Don't run it in too much.  You know what they say about paybacks.  ?
great job gentleman!!! Scott, your little brotha is kickin' your butt!!!  that first fish is rather large for the upper....but I know you guys sure know what your doing on that body of water!
I know.....1st trip for him there he gets 2 ha!  Like to see him repeat it.  We'll find out soon enough.
